{"tid":2306351,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"占奔：到了今天，我仍然覺得伍公子未收皮是一件荒誕事。","createTime":"2020-11-30T11:18:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T13:48:30.000Z","uid":154872,"like":21,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"42ca5d8ab80d35ada8f67e083539c77150eb489d","tid":2306351,"uid":154872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T11:18:11.000Z","msg":"如題。<br />\n<br />\n占奔睇了牠的貼文，可以基本確認牠不是有心想平反，而是想達成目標如下所示：<br />\n<br />\n1. 作為一隻attention whore，近牌冇人比佢抽水，冇content下又拎返舊事出嚟講了；<br />\n<br />\n2. 想搵佢口中嘅連登仔一戰，然後又cap圖炒下抽下水；<br />\n<br />\n3. 或者想連登仔記返起佢，太耐冇人提過伍公子。<br />\n<br />\nAngela其實都放低咗，唔明伍公子諗緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，伍犬幾時死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed09af348212da150e0e8fb481dcef4cc42e801b","tid":2306351,"uid":154872,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T11:20:09.000Z","msg":"btw波台迷袁黨已各散東西了嗎？"},{"pid":"a123d29da04615b56a08548a971892e2411da55e","tid":2306351,"uid":101699,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ed09af348212da150e0e8fb481dcef4cc42e801b","tid":2306351,"uid":154872,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T11:20:09.000Z","msg":"btw波台迷袁黨已各散東西了嗎？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T11:22:11.000Z","msg":"迷袁黨天字第一號會員在此<br />\n隻伍乞衣人人得而誅之<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25cd86997d3e1f7d8fd65856b228622679babd46","tid":2306351,"uid":134997,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T11:24:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"656116529b2163c5481c1ab9a9917f091dda8d4d","tid":2306351,"uid":311309,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T11:24:43.000Z","msg":"伍乞兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52f4feabd5de3f2047b1de7dffad23cf931edd24","tid":2306351,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T11:26:34.000Z","msg":"伍乞兒<img src=\"/asset